WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.939
Smurf knows that you talked to the cops.

00:01.940 --> 00:04.122
If you stay here, you will be killed.

00:04.123 --> 00:05.832
My brother's kind of strange.

00:05.833 --> 00:07.289
What's the hole out in the field?

00:07.290 --> 00:09.400
- A bunker.
- Jed's stockpiling gold.

00:10.980 --> 00:13.710
What's back there, baby?

00:13.716 --> 00:15.092
I have a job for us.

00:15.093 --> 00:17.345
And this time, I will be joining you.

00:17.360 --> 00:21.219
You boys have been having all
the fun for way too long.

00:21.220 --> 00:22.239
Smurf up?

00:22.240 --> 00:24.686
She left with some people
from La Jolla last night.

00:24.690 --> 00:26.938
- Where is it?
- What?

00:29.560 --> 00:31.239
You're done with that shit.

00:31.240 --> 00:32.651
You think I wanted this to happen?

00:32.652 --> 00:34.528
J took me to Kalani's for lunch...

00:34.529 --> 00:36.539
- 'Sup, Pope?
- I'm looking for Angela.

00:36.540 --> 00:37.919
Have you seen her?

00:37.920 --> 00:40.701
Yesterday. She was with Julia's kid.

00:40.702 --> 00:42.953
You didn't forget about seeing Angela.

00:42.954 --> 00:45.831
- You just keep lying to me, J.
- Pope, it's...

00:45.832 --> 00:47.874
When Smurf's gone, so are you.

00:47.900 --> 00:49.620
Back, back!

00:53.540 --> 00:55.299
Colin? Hey!

00:55.300 --> 00:56.920
- Colin?
- He's dead, Janine.

